<plot>A teacher named Chen Yi-Shing took his class to a field trip in the mountain and encountered huge wasp attack on the way. Unable to escape, the teacher exposed himself naked to the horrible wasps' stings and sacrificed his own life in order to save his students. This film is based on a true tragic event that happened in the '80s. It's one of the most graphically horrifying film made in Taiwan.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?101655</url></doc>
